CallFire,is,an,online,text,and,voice,messaging,platform,designed,to,meet,the,needs,of,a,variety,of,users,and,organizations,The,platform,comes,with,APIs,for,integrating,its,functions,into,third,party,applications,and,services,The,Voice,Broadcast,API,allows,users,to,upload,and,broadcast,recorded,message,files,in,either,WAV,or,MP,format